data.title: Pennington Co. Courant, November 1, 2012
data.meta_description: Pennington Co. Courant, November 1, 2012 - Free download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. Pennington County firefighters held their annual recognition and awards banquet on saturday night, October 20 at the new underwood community center. It is held yearly to recognize The Pennington County Firefighter and Pennington County fire Officer of the year and to pay their respects to firefighters who have passed away the past year. This year there were four Firefighter nominees, Kristofer laRoche, rapid valley vfd; duane
